Gah.

62
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:30,940
Take a look, Bajie. Can you see?

63
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:33,940
Many of your good friends are here.

64
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:37,940
We're just fair-weather friends, that's all.

65
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:41,940
But they are still friends, aren't they?

66
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:44,940
So you say, so it must be.

67
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:49,940
These old buddies...

68
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:52,940
I think none of them ended up well.

69
