76
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:18,940
Fortune is simply...

77
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:21,940
Humility in the mighty.

78
00:05:21,940 --> 00:05:23,940
Well, mayhaps.

79
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:26,940
They simply lacked my charm.

80
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:33,940
Gifted they may be, yet strive they not.

81
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:37,940
Content with little, and lost in lust.

82
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:41,940
Seek the ease, yet crave the renown.

83
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:45,940
They yearn for freedom, yet aspire to Buddhahood.

84
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:47,940
They always want both.

85
